<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>1017</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ruò bù shì yé hé huá bāng zhù wǒ men, wǒ men zěn néng shēng cún? shì
 ruò bù shì yé hé huá bāng zhù wǒ men, wǒ men zěn néng qián jìn? shì
 xiàn shàng gǎn ēn de, xīn jìng bài dú yī zhēn shén.
 zhǔ yǐ dé jiù de lè gē, sì miàn huán rào wǒ men. sì miàn huán rào wǒ men.
 dà de yě zài qīng tīng, fēng ér yě sòng gěi piāo xiàng yuǎn fāng de yún.
 wàn guó wàn zú de rén, dōu yào bēn pǎo cháo jiàn shén. zhè lǐ shì tiān de mén.</lyrics>
<title>ruò bù shì yé hé huá bāng zhù wǒ men 迦南1017</title>
</song>